Package org.hibernate.mapping

Class RootClass

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.mapping.PersistentClass
org.hibernate.mapping.RootClass
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, AttributeContainer, Contributable, Filterable, IdentifiableTypeClass, MetaAttributable, SoftDeletable, TableContainer, TableOwner
public final class RootClass extends PersistentClass implements TableOwner, SoftDeletable
A mapping model object that represents the root class in an entity class inheritance hierarchy.
